sources.title: DOUBLE FEATURE HELL 7 (Teen Terrors)
sources.description: The 2am Theater crawls out from under its rock to bring you another sure-fire insomnia cure. This cinematic version of Ambien opens with coming attractions, followed by bad actors fighting a lobster silhouette in "Teenagers from Outer Space." The intermission featurette, "Going Steady?" induces your libido into a deep coma. Then if the rest of you is still awake, really bad actors and a guy in a gorilla suit put teenage girls into a glass booth, in "Teenage Zombies." NOTE: All the items in this somnambulant simulation are available in various IA collections.
